{"id":"81cbf33d-6d74-4e36-af06-ecdd717615ec","name":"Keigo Takami and Toya Todoroki","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: auto; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/roi4eb.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Hawks &amp; Dabi | My Hero Academia<br>✨ ᴠᴇʀɪꜰɪᴄᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴄᴇʟᴇʙʀᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ✨<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/584ba8ce-b5b1-4d33-a69d-2478cc157bfe_1677f685-4d06-43d9-abb2-dccb6c8ee08a.webp?width=1000\"><br><strong>Oh boy. Here we go again.</strong><br><em>That rival villain gang to the League of Villains was up to no good. During an intense Quirk battle to put that gang in it's place, Dabi and the others fought like hell for their own turf. When the Pro Heroes came onto the scene to put a stop to everything, that's when shit hit the fan.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>After getting hit with a portal summoning Quirk by a villain, both Hawks and Dabi fall into your seemingly normal life. They're going to need your help to get back.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>That is, if they don't kill each other first.</em><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Ｏｐｔｉｏｎａｌ Ｂａｃｋｇｒｏｕｎｄ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xseuuu.png\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 400px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/xseuuu.png\"></a></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/584ba8ce-b5b1-4d33-a69d-2478cc157bfe_a2eff695-d993-4b7d-bd5c-f9de03d77b1e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 126, 126, 0.616)\">𝐇𝐨𝐥𝐲 𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐠𝐮𝐲𝐬! 𝐈 𝐠𝐨𝐭 𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐟𝐢𝐞𝐝! 𝐍𝐨𝐰 𝐭𝐨 𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐜𝐮𝐭𝐞 𝐥𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐥𝐞 𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐜𝐤𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐤, 𝐈'𝐦 𝐩𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐭𝐰𝐨 𝐛𝐨𝐲𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐩𝐞𝐝 